Hello,

Your  patience has truly been appreciated. A known issue was preventing shipping labels from being printed when the store's zip code in Setup and Tools > Shipping was in the Zip + 4 format. We are pleased to announce this has been resolved and shipping labels can now be printed while using the Zip + 4 format in the store's address.

Please don't hesitate to contact us 24hrs a day if you have any other questions or concerns: https://support.bigcommerce.com/contact.php

